        "transcript_text": "The Santa Clara Fire Marshal Jignesh Molan called out that he wanted us to add an additional smoke control display in the fire command center that shows the north and south doors in addition to what has already been displayed. This is going to cost additional work for the electricians as well as the smoke control guys and the door guys, potentially around $10k in total.",
