        "local_audio_uri": "file:///var/mobile/Containers/Data/Application/171121ED-FC13-410A-8985-271D6F0AC7D8/Documents/audio/recording_1767991247955_ry28934c6zimk7cc9qs.m4a",
        "transcript_text": "We just discovered that the building management system BMS wasn't properly metering the air handling units on the roof, which means that we're going to have technicians come out and take a look. We just had a meeting about this with the electricians as well as the BMS people. So now they're going to have to call their technicians to come out and take a look at these. This will have to be followed up on and we need to make sure that all the meters are functioning properly.",
